+### `app.getCurrentPictureInPicture()`
+
+Returns `VideoPictureInPicture | DocumentPictureInPicture | null` - A handle
+for the active Picture-in-Picture window, or `null` if no video or Document
+Picture-in-Picture window is active.
+
+The returned object is tied to the PiP session that created it. If the PiP
+window is closed and another PiP window is opened later, methods on the old
+handle will not affect the new PiP window.
